\mathbb E(X)=\int_0^{+\infty}\mathbb P\{X>t\}\mathrm dt,
\mathbb E(\xi\chi_{\{\xi>a\}})=a\mathbb P\{\xi>a\}+\int_a^{+\infty}\mathbb P\{\xi>t\}\mathrm dt.
